Description: Tech4LessWholesale Store PLEASE READ BEFORE BIDDING: Please check the IMEI/ESN if you intend to activate, we do not check with the carrier if the IMEI/ESN can be successfully activated (see pictures for IMEI/ESN number). We ask you to do this since there is not a way for us to get this info for you and have it be 100% accurate. Please contact us before bidding if you have questions or do not understand. Most of our phones are ready to activate, but we want you to feel good about it before purchasing and know it can be activated. Great for resale or personal use. Unit powers up with good LCD, working touch and has been data wiped. No further testing performed. Listing comes with a untested battery and back cover. Does not include original accessories or chargers. Our Mission Statement: We feel it would be helpful to share more about us, so that you can better understand our product and our intentions when we list on eBay. We are specifically a wholesale company. It is rarely our intention to try and sell each and every phone, one at a time, to individual buyers on eBay. Our intent is to sell to people interested in doing the final testing and selling of each and every device. Checking the ESN, checking Wi-Fi, the camera, etc., the last few steps. We understand that if we sold each and every phone, fully tested, with a charger, that we might get up to 500% more for each device. But that is not our current desire or business model. We receive thousands of phones monthly and limit our testing because of lack of time and manpower. When we say a phone has been tested to: power up, with a good LCD and working touch screen and it has been data wiped we DO NOT mean that the device is most likely to have some type of issue. We mean that we only have the time to test this much on each phone. On the whole, about 80% of our cell phones work perfectly fine when people buy consistently or in our larger lots. Sometimes that working percentage gets up to 90%, it just depends on that batch of product. In each and every marketplace there is a manufacturer, a wholesaler and a final retailer. Our intention is to be the wholesaler. Not the retailer. We are happy to support dozens of buyers on eBay that buy regularly from us, in large numbers, and turn around and sell those same devices, one at a time, on eBay or in a retail setting. We are fully aware this happens each day and are looking for more people to buy from us, test our product and resell and make the additional money that is out there. It is good for you to know phones, how to test quickly and how to validate an ESN/IMEI. We get plenty of people asking each day if a certain cell phone takes a SIM card. An excellent research tool to use is PhoneScoop.com if you are unfamiliar with a particular model. Do not jump right into buying used phones thinking it's easy and all of us make a ton of money. It is hard, it takes time, energy, resources and good people. We do sell products in other ways but have been happy to find buyers on eBay that come back weekly or daily, and buy more. Thank you all for your repeat business. May we all grow wealthy together. Best regards and happy bidding.

Title: Apple iPhone 4s - 16GB - White (AT&T) Smartphone
Description: Detailed item infoProduct InformationThe Apple iPhone 4S is rich with technology and features for an enhanced user experience. The release of the iPhone 4 had smartphone users impressed, thanks to state-of-the-art size, speed, and applications. Apple topped the iPhone 4 with the Apple iPhone 4S, which builds on the iPhone 4 for an even better user experience. Along with a more powerful chip and an improved camera the Apple iPhone 4S also includes an interactive personal assistant to help keep busy lives running smoothly. Meet Siri This 4S smartphone boasts the all-new Siri application which introduces a new level of interactive software. This personal assistant is prepared to assist and guide on any one of the many tasks that face users every day. It can understand speakers without any formatting requirement for questions and commands, so users can converse with it as they would with another person. From directions to reminders to initiating calls and much more, Siri offers constant support for many tasks. Now emails and text messages can be dictated while driving for safer travel, and with a simple request, Siri will play the song you want to hear, search the Web, dial a call, or schedule a meeting. Experience the Dual-Core A5 Chip. The Apple iPhone 4S has the most powerful chip ever included in an iPhone; the dual-core A5. Double cores mean double power, as well as graphics that are up to seven times faster. Now do anything on the iPhone 4S with lightning speed, including gaming, launching applications, and browsing the Web. The A5 chip gives this Apple smartphone an exceptionally long battery life. Advanced Camera The camera of the Apple iPhone 4S might very well make stand-alone digital cameras obsolete. Eight megapixels have full capacity to collect unprecedented amounts of light. As a result, it delivers images with significantly improved detail and resolution, which carries through perfectly in enlargements up to 8x10. Besides the increase in megapixels has been completely re-engineered and upgraded to provide an excellent image regardless of the amount of light available. This Apple smartphone has a custom lens that shapes incoming light with five precision elements. This gives each image a sharper quality that is not seen in any earlier Apple smartphone camera. A backside illumination sensor offers additional sensitivity, resulting in crisp and clear photos. The iPhone 4S offers an automatic LED flash for low-light situations which can also be manually powered. The secret behind the technology of the Apple iPhone 4S camera is the A5 chip and the iOS 5 platform. Users can control exposure on the Apple iPhone 4S just as they would on a standard digital camera and tap to focus. Editing, cropping, enhancing, and red-eye removal all happen right on the device, which means it's able to correct and send photos moments after they happen. Quality Video All the new features of the iPhone 4S camera make videos better as well. Whether there is ample light or barely any at all, an advanced backside illumination sensor and a bigger aperture are prepared to make the most of what is available. Video stabilization is state-of-the-art for a smartphone, so movies are great even when the videographer's hands are unsteady. There are more than 200 new features on this 4S smartphone, making it easy to upgrade. Text messaging is taken to an entirely new level with iMessage, offering secure, unlimited instant conversations with any other iOS5 iPhone user. Twitter is integrated directly into the iOS 5 platform, making tweets faster and easier than ever. Overall, the iPhone 4S is a super enhanced improvisation of the iPhone 4 by Apple. Enhancements to existing features, along with a variety of new ones, make the decision to upgrade to Apple iPhone 4S an easy one.

Title: Apple iPhone 5 - 16GB - Black & Slate (Unlocked) GREAT CONDITION
Description: Detailed item info Product Information When Apple envisioned the iPhone, Apple landed on a remarkably thin and light design. But it's nearly impossible to make a device so thin and so light without sacrificing features or performance. Apple could have taken the easy way out and designed something more reasonable and less remarkable. But Apple didn't. If the technology didn't exist, Apple invented it. If a component wasn't small enough, Apple re-imagined it. If convention was standing in the way, Apple left it behind. The result is iPhone 5: the thinnest, lightest, fastest iPhone ever. iPhone 5 is just 7.6 millimeters thin. To make that happen, Apple engineers had to think small, component by component. They created a nano-SIM card, which is 44 percent smaller than a micro-SIM. They also developed a unique cellular solution for iPhone 5. The conventional approach to building LTE into a world phone uses two chips - one for voice, one for data. On iPhone 5, both are on a single chip. The intelligent, reversible Lightning connector is 80 percent smaller than the 30-pin connector. The 8-megapixel iSight camera has even more features - like panorama and dynamic low-light mode - yet it's 20 percent smaller. And the A6 chip is up to 2x faster than the A5 chip but 22 percent smaller. Title: Apple iPhone 4s - 16GB - Black (Sprint) Smartphone for parts
Description: Hi there! I am selling my sons used Iphone 4s black from the Sprint Network. It does work, however it has some issues which I will describe here so that you can decide if you want it for parts or wish to have it repaired etc. The HOME button does not work. Basically you have to push the top botton on the top (side) of the phone to "activate" the phone but there are times you need to push the home button...so it is a problem that it is not working. Also, I cannot seem to power it off. Therefore it just stays on until it completely dies or you plug it in and charge it more. Otherwise, it does work and does have a clean MEID # (which you can see in one of the photos here of the phone and you can call Spring and verify it is good and clean before you purchase it if you like :) I dod have the original box but do not have the charging cord or headset or manual that came with the phone. This auction is for the phone itself and the box. That's it. Please see my feedback and bid with confidence as I am always honest and fair with all my Ebay transactions. Paypal only please. Shipping by USPS Priority Mail. NOTE: I will charge it up before I ship it to you but because I cannot turn it off (as described above), it will most likely arrive to you with a depleted battery. You will need to plug it in once you receive it to charge it up again. p.s. Screen and phone are in good shape. I noticed one very minor chip on left side of the phone....which is barely noticeable actually. Screen is smudged...lol...but thats it. Screen is NOT cracked and back of phone is also in super nice shape. Battery life (once charged) is good, but not great, I must say. If you play music on it for example.....and run the battery down, you will need to recharge by plugging it in.
